The paper deals with the automatic analysis of microscopy images using computer vision and pattern recognition methodologies. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. Additionally, the paper involves the use of machine learning algorithms for classification and detection, which could also place it in the machine learning (cs.LG) sub-category. The use of feature extraction and pattern recognition techniques could also suggest the information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category. The paper also involves the use of image processing techniques, which could place it in the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category. Finally, the use of algorithms for detecting and classifying objects could suggest the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category.
